        {
            "title": "黃金市場｜不得吹捧黃金交易 禁以黃金名義非法集資 深圳進一步規範黃金市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EEfJ9XjJhBIKco_lX1sW4g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/1dff9ea44b3011eb6a54f386db5f4ff8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最近貴金屬炒賣成風加上深圳水貝金銀交易市場杰我睿「爆煲」，深圳市地方金融管理局發公告進一步規範深圳市黃金市場經營秩序，就從事黃金業務的企業或個人進一步限制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據最新發表的公告，企業不得使用「黃金會大漲」、「買金賺大錢」等用語作宣傳，不得誇大投資回報和進行任何槓桿或延遲交易等非法黃金交易活動等；企業業不得透過微信群組或其他互聯網平台，允許客戶繳付一定金額保證金鎖定一定重量黃金價格，後隨金價波動按價差結算，但未實際開展黃金實物交割。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f189c264-84fe-3778-9567-b00c4155caea-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個人不得組織或者參與以黃金名義的非法集資或非法黃金投資等業務，當中不能開發兜售非法黃金交易軟件或平台。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金融機構需要向相關部門備案才可開展黃金業務，不得違反大額交易及可疑交易報告制度和開展非法黃金活動等宣傳。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上月底位於深圳水具的金銀交易市場「杰我睿」貴金屬投資公司疑「爆煲」，客戶出現無法提取或限制提取的情況，事件涉及近百億元和15萬名投資者受影響，羅湖區政府已經介入進行調查。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E5%90%B9%E6%8D%A7%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A5%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%90%8D%E7%BE%A9%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E8%B3%87-%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E8%A6%8F%E7%AF%84%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-093000111.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 17:31:45",
